          "name": "Springhill Suites - In Marriott Village at Lake Buena Vista",
          "virginView": "The Marriott Village is a wonderful combination of 3 quality hotels in 1 resort, giving you the benefit of facilities at all 3 hotels for 1 great price! Each hotel gives you a different experience, with the SpringHill Suites offering studio apartment feel with a combined bedroom and living area, great for families and the extra space means you won't feel like you're on top of each other. There is&#xa0;complimentary shuttle access to selected parks, and a free buffet breakfast to fuel the whole family before a day exploring. The superb dining and entertainment choices of Lake Buena Vista and Disney Springs are only minutes away, while the resort has its own Village Marketplace Food Court should you not feel like venturing out. Whichever hotel you decide best suits you, you'll know that you're in a great location near to both Walt Disney World Resort and Universal Orlando&#xae; Resort, with one of Florida's best premium outlet malls on your doorstep!",
